-------------------------------------------------------------------
     
                        openMDX/WebLogic

-------------------------------------------------------------------

1/ What this guide is for
   ----------------------

   This distribution contains WebLogic-specific extensions for openMDX.


2/ Java Archives
   -------------

   * WebLogic ClassPath
     openmdx-kernel.jar 
     openmdx-weblogic.security.jar
   * Alternate WebLogic MBean Directory  
     openmdx-weblogic.mbean.jar  

     
3/ System Properties
   -----------------
   
   * java.protocol.handler.pkgs
     org.openmdx.kernel.url.protocol     
   * weblogic.alternateTypesDirectory
     ...
   * org.openmdx.log.path
     ...
   * org.openmdx.log.config.filename
     ...


4/ Authentication Providers
   ------------------------

   AirLock
   * Insert an AirLockIdentityAsserter instance at the first position.
   
   
5/ Secure Web Applications
   -----------------------
   
    <login-config>
      <auth-method>CLIENT-CERT</auth-method>
      <realm-name>...</realm-name>
    </login-config>

---
End of README
